These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, aristoff
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the aristoff-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | aristoff   | fonseca  |
| Sport   | soccer | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lemon
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian
1. the mexican is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the mexican is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apple | lemon      |
| Pet    | mexican  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
