.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, paramedic
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster
1. the paramedic is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the paramedic is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2      |
| Food   | project-manager  | paramedic |
| Pet    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, superhero
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, collecting
1. the person watching superhero movies is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | superhero |
| Sport         | collecting | photography      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
