.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, roller
2 different pets are kept: goat, hamster
1. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the train is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | train | roller |
| Pet   | goat       | hamster       |

