.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-20::.
2 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the owner of the hedgehog##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | dog      |
| Sport   | fishing | hiking |

 